snippet.title: Under - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Under is a horror game set in the early 20th century. Alexander Dockter is a WW1 veteran who must escape a sinking oceanliner, but he's not alone below decks. Under is coming to PC and consoles later this year.

#ign #gaming
